data.description: Newer Home For Sale!  Must See!  This beautiful Lennar home is in the Candelas Community in the Southeast side of Visalia.  The homes here are part of the popular California Series.  You will love what this attractive 1,580 sqft home has to offer, it's an open floor-plan, 3 bedrooms, 2 bath of comfortable living space sitting on a 6,970 lot.  This home also features an office/den, indoor laundry and two car garage.  Built in 2020, this home includes a leased solar system making this home energy efficient.  You'll enjoy the modern open living room, dining room, and nice island kitchen with beautiful granite counter tops.  The appliances include a stove, dishwasher, and built-in microwave.  As you make your way through the house you will notice the bedrooms are spacious with the indoor laundry conveniently located in the hallway.  Once you enter the huge master suite, you will appreciate the very spacious bathroom and walk-in closet.  Wait till you see the size of the backyard, it's perfect for entertaining.  You do not want to wait on this one.
